# Git Ignore
# Block everything by default in sensitive folders, except templates

# 1. Settings
SETTINGS.md

# 2. Trackers (Ignore active, keep templates)
BUGS/*.md
!BUGS/*_TEMPLATE.md

CRITICAL/*.md
!CRITICAL/*_TEMPLATE.md

PROJECTS/*.md
!PROJECTS/*_TEMPLATE.md

PEOPLE/*.md
!PEOPLE/*_TEMPLATE.md

# 3. Products (Ignore context files, keep readme/templates)
PRODUCTS/*.md
!PRODUCTS/README.md
!PRODUCTS/*_TEMPLATE.md
# Keep examples if explicitly tracked (git handles this, but good to be explicit if we wanted)

# 4. Data / Inbox / Meetings
_INBOX/**/*
!_INBOX/.gitkeep

MEETINGS/**/*.md
!MEETINGS/**/.gitkeep

00_drop_files_here00/
RESEARCH/
STRATEGY/
FEATURES/

# 5. System
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
